					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## 4) Tool `#description` JSON examples "
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [
						{
							"__type" : "textSnippet",
							"children" : {
								"__type" : "snippets",
								"items" : [ ]
							},
							"createEmail" : {
								"__type" : "email",
								"emailString" : "<unknown>"
							},
							"createTime" : {
								"__type" : "time",
								"time" : {
									"__type" : "dateAndTime",
									"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-06T11:51:44.285232+01:00"
								}
							},
							"editEmail" : {
								"__type" : "email",
								"emailString" : "<unknown>"
							},
							"editTime" : {
								"__type" : "time",
								"time" : {
									"__type" : "dateAndTime",
									"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-06T11:53:01.981081+01:00"
								}
							},
							"uid" : {
								"__type" : "uid",
								"uidString" : "/6RlndS0Q7OojOBfAblM3w=="
							},
							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "Create examples in a `*Examples` class in {{gtPackage:Gt4LlmCore-Examples}}:\n\n**Tool examples:**\n- Success case: assert the result is {{gtClass:GtLMagritteBasedModel}} and the model is the expected domain object with stable values.\n- Missing argument: assert {{gtClass:GtLMissingArgumentDomainObject}}.\n- Missing resource: assert {{gtClass:GtLMissingDomainObject}} when applicable.\n- `mayHaveMore` case: use a **stable high-cardinality input** (see below).\n\n**Domain object examples:**\n- Creation example verifying all fields.\n- Serialization example using {{gtClass:GtMagritteJSONDataExporter}} with **concrete values** in the expected JSON object.\n\n### Stable inputs for `mayHaveMore` tests (new)\nUse inputs known to yield large results:\n- Class search: `Object`\n- Method implementors: `gtDisplayOn:`\n- Package classes: `Bloc`\n- Substring literal search: `gt`\n\nAvoid asserting `mayHaveMore` is false unless the input is guaranteed to stay small.\n"
						}
					]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
